Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是最重要的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:59.16,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}翻譯 小舌 校譯 洛艾妖 時間 倉鼠 後期 DK  壓制 克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz-3\pos(475,62)}小雪和由乃結合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小雪結合的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}不履行契約
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs28\an5\pos(412,287)}三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前來的時候我記得電和水都被停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是自己又連上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正世界就要毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都無法抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所有都會完結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在泡澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起泡吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 是泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定以為我什麼都沒穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊 小雪的假話很容易被看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等哦 我現在就重新燒水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡是每天都要洗的哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的持有人已經都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用擔心會被殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人不能復活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能大家才是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊的是由乃才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她為什麼要說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也想殺掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存遊戲的贏家只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃怎麼會殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\fs28\pos(429,378)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs25\frz13\pos(641,145)}[我妻家 廚房前]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs25\frz12\pos(703,164)}由乃在廚房叫我。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(660,200)}好像有什麼事情要我過去。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(672,230)}[我妻家 廚房前]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(445,340)}由乃邀我一起泡澡。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(644,329)}[我妻家 院子]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(491,422)}由乃和往常一樣在劈柴。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是在懷疑由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是繼續檢查日記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著把你塞進爸爸的浴衣裡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 今天一起去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等… 這個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泡澡的時候不帶著日記太不謹慎了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是個只懂殺戮的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我或許沒什麼魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等全部結束了 我以為你會愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪卻完全不把我當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為這樣 才邀我一起洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃她是說喜歡我…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻想殺我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃真的想殺掉我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會的話 明明隨時可以殺掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼面對由乃才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不明白自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次跟你講話是在教室裡呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃只剩下小雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃都會一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看著小雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
